    <item>
      <title>英特尔将为亚马逊生产定制 AI 芯片，推迟德国工厂建设</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/intel-to-make-custom-ai-chip-for-amazon-delay-german-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔公司首席执行官帕特·基辛格已将亚马逊公司的 AWS 作为该公司制造业务的客户，这可能会给美国在建的新工厂带来工作，并加大他扭转这家陷入困境的芯片制造商的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/intel-to-make-custom-ai-chip-for-amazon-delay-german-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 20:01:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英特尔确认向五角大楼提供 30 亿美元芯片资助；股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/intel-confirms-3-billion-defense-department-chips-act-grant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔公司周一表示，它有资格获得高达 30 亿美元的美国政府资助，用于生产军用芯片，证实了彭博社早些时候的报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/intel-confirms-3-billion-defense-department-chips-act-grant</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 19:01:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛交易部门表示现在是逢低买入人工智能股票的时候了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/goldman-trading-desk-says-it-s-time-to-buy-the-dip-in-ai-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人工智能相关股票最近受到重创，但随着利率下降且基本面保持强劲，高盛集团的交易部门认为现在是逢低买入的时候。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/goldman-trading-desk-says-it-s-time-to-buy-the-dip-in-ai-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 18:43:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金融科技公司 Cherry 推出与先买后付整容手术贷款挂钩的债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/fintech-cherry-pitches-bond-tied-to-buy-now-pay-later-cosmetic-surgery-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，随着医疗债务需求激增，支付公司 Cherry Technologies 正在向投资者征询意见，希望发行一种与整容手术和其他美容治疗的“先买后付”贷款挂钩的债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/fintech-cherry-pitches-bond-tied-to-buy-now-pay-later-cosmetic-surgery-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 18:25:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊 CEO 誓言精简团队以应对臃肿员工，并结束在家办公</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/amazon-ceo-wants-workers-in-five-days-a-week-leaner-management</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司首席执行官安迪·贾西 (Andy Jassy) 正在采取措施精简这家全球最大的在线零售商和云计算公司，削减管理层级，并要求员工从 1 月份开始每周五天返回办公室工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/amazon-ceo-wants-workers-in-five-days-a-week-leaner-management</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 17:41:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙正在谈判赢得法国关键的欧盟委员会职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/macron-in-talks-to-win-pivotal-job-for-sejourne-at-eu-commission</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙正在与欧盟委员会进行谈判，为法国开辟一个新的、更强大的职位，他的提名人将负责监督欧盟为提升其竞争力所做的所有努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/macron-in-talks-to-win-pivotal-job-for-sejourne-at-eu-commission</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 15:44:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 因抗议美国禁令而受到法庭严厉质询</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/tiktok-appeal-of-us-ban-over-china-ties-to-be-argued-in-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从上诉法院小组的质询来看，如果中国所有者不出售这款广受欢迎的社交媒体应用，TikTok 将面临一场艰难的战斗，以避开美国的禁令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/tiktok-appeal-of-us-ban-over-china-ties-to-be-argued-in-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
